{"tid":124633,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)奇謀妙計五福星 福星高照","createTime":"2017-02-17T18:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T21:48:07.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28eaaa63c12cb7be86b9e9340f319ab988dcda86","tid":124633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:10:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rangdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2b234c46\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rangdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=bd1c01df\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/71/Winners-and-sinners-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F71%2FWinners-and-sinners-poster.jpg&h=74de982e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fe/My_Lucky_Stars.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffe%2FMy_Lucky_Stars.jpg&h=e75b84fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奇謀妙計五福星:茶壺、死氣喉、凡士林、鬈毛積及劉克司五人出獄後決改邪歸正，與鬈毛積之妹(妹頭)同組「五寶清潔公司」。某次匪徒正交易偽鈔電版時遇劫匪，剛巧被 CID 看見便一路追趕，後劫匪情急下將電版拋進五福星之清潔車中。 五寶開始被兩大反派追殺，最後五福星施展奇謀妙計應付兩大反派。<br />\n<br />\n福星高照:一個腐敗的香港警察三哥（林正英）攜帶大批鑽石財寶去了日本投靠了黑幫「稻草人俱樂部」。瑞奇和大力丸（成龍）奉命追至日本緝拿，他們在地鐵發現了三哥，並且去追，追到遊樂場，三哥的接應人日本黑幫前來阻擋，三哥被走脫了，而瑞奇被黑幫一棍子打昏，抓了起來。雞骨草打了個電話，叫曹警司（曹達華）叫鷓鴣菜前來日本幫忙。<br />\n鷓鴣菜此時在香港監獄關著，曹警司叫手下監獄官（田俊）將他釋放，結果他才到公路上不久，再次行竊又被抓了。曹警官控訴他「逃獄」，但是只要他將功折罪去日本幫忙抓三哥......<br />\n<br />\n2 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d920cf38106c5a5c9cb1bd50a9f973010f5975e","tid":124633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ccc5e909d0c1d0823827600c6a5914b3c495ba","tid":124633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d453f71f79d2dff7bd0cf95af60ff0966670c9b2","tid":124633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T20:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50711ab7e039a416801ad1ab053c8cfa4b5b58b4","tid":124633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T21:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ffb35272cf08f9414a49fee866bfe76c6a77a9","tid":124633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T21:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}